  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"rank\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-rank\"></span>\n<h1>rank<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#rank\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">rank</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/tensor/attribute.py#L37\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Returns the number of dimensions for a tensor, which is a 0-D int32 Tensor.</p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p><strong>input</strong> (<em>Tensor</em>) – The input Tensor with shape of <span class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\\([N_1, N_2, ..., N_k]\\)</span>, the data type is arbitrary.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">\n           Returns\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\">\n<p>The 0-D tensor with the dimensions of the input Tensor.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Return type\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p>Tensor, the output data type is int32.</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">\n<pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">paddle</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">input</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rand</span><span class=\"p\">((</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">rank</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rank</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">input</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rank</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">numpy</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"go\">3</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>"
